==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Perseid
<hw>Per"se*id</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Perseus</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Astron.)</fld> <def>One of a group of shooting stars which appear yearly about the 10th of August, and cross the heavens in paths apparently radiating from the constellation <etsep>Perseus</etsep>.  They are probably fragments of Swift's comet of 1862 (III).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Perseus</ent>⟦br⟧
